metadata.name: Tsar Alexander #1
metadata.description: Project Gallanthians is formed by our British company, which is managed by professionals and a skilled team with an extensive background in blockchain technology. The goal of our company is to create synergy between technology, art and entertainment at the highest level. That is why we have decided to connect NFT technology with the gaming world. Our vision consists of creating a unique gaming environment at the highest level across all gaming devices and platforms, which will provide the opportunity to play a plethora of different characters and mystical beings. Our game will not only provide a detailed artistic perspective but also an educational take, where a player will be able to learn and understand the hero they will be playing.
